### Local Image

~~~ .php
Image::open('.\path\to\photo.jpg')
    ->crop(72)
    ->saveAs('photo-2.jpg');
~~~

### Remote Image

~~~ .php
Image::open('http://example.com/image.jpg')
    ->crop(72)
    ->saveAs('photo-2.jpg');
~~~

### Base64 Image

~~~ .php
Image::open('data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD …')
    ->crop(72)
    ->saveAs('photo-2.jpg');
~~~

